The paper discusses congestion control techniques in high speed networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Other possible sub-categories include cs.COMM (Communication and Information Theory), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
